about.aboutContent:
Plan your next day in Greater Sudbury!


Feel free to explore the city with the aid of this web map.

Help:
Using the widgets located on the sidebar to the left of your screen, you are able to toggle layers on/off, obtain directions to one or multiple locations in series, and measure distances between points.
On the top left of your screen is a link to the City of Greater Sudbury's website where you can keep up to date with current events and more of what Sudbury has to offer.
More information about the points of interest found on this map can be found in the attribute table at the of this map.
